 Windows Update Troubleshooting Lab

## Objective
Diagnose and fix Windows Update failures using standard troubleshooting steps.

## Tools
- Windows 10 VM (VirtualBox)  
- Command Prompt  
- Windows Update utility

## Steps
1. Stopped Windows Update and BITS services  
2. Cleared the SoftwareDistribution cache  
3. Restarted services  
4. Verified updates installed successfully

## Result
Windows Update restored; system can now receive updates reliably.

## Key Takeaways
- Managed Windows services via command line  
- Practiced systematic troubleshooting  
- Reinforced real-world Windows admin skills

